\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7822487 \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Teach me to step aright in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6177181\charrsid1317583 \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37  the way of Christ's commandments. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Strengthen me to keep awake in song, and drive away the sleep of despondency. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Bride of God, by thy prayers release me, bound with the bonds of sin.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Guard \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 me by night and by day, and deliver me from foes that defeat me.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O bearer of God the Life-giver, enliven me who am deadened by passions.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O bearer of the unwaning Light, enlighten my blinded soul.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O marvelous palace of the Master, make me to be a house of t\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 he Divine Spirit.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O bearer of the Healer, heal the perennial passions of my soul.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Guide me to the path of repentance, for I am tossed in the storm of life.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Deliver me from eternal fire, and from evil worms, and from Tartarus.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Let me not be exposed to the r\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 ejoicing of demons, guilty as I am of many sins.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Renew me, grown old from senseless sins, O most immaculate one.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Present me untouched by all torments, and pray for me to the Master of all.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Vouchsafe me to find the joys of heaven with all the saints.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O most\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37  holy Virgin, hearken unto the voice of thine unprofitable servant.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Grant me torrents of tears, O most pure one, to cleanse my soul from impurity.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 I offer the groans of my heart to thee unceasingly, strive for me, O Sovereign Lady.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Accept my service of sup\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 plication and offer it to compassionate God.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O thou who art above the angels, raise me above this world's confusion.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Light bearing heavenly tabernacle, direct the grace of the Spirit in me.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 I raise my hands and lips in thy praise, defiled as they are by impurity, O all immaculate one. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Deliver me from soul corrupting evils, and fervently intercede with Christ, to Whom \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 is due honor and worship, now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
