\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Give no place for the cunning demon to master me through the violence of my mortal body, strengthen my poor and feeble ha\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 nd, and guide me in the way of salvation. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 Yea, O holy angel of God, guardian and protector of my wretched soul and body, forgive me all wherein I have offended thee all the days of my life; and if I have sinned during the past night, protect me during the
\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37  present day, and guard me from every temptation of the enemy, that I may not anger God by any sin. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 And pray to the Lord for me, that He may establish me in His fear, and show me, His servant, to be worthy of His goodness. Amen.
